data.title: What were the major defeats of the Ottoman Empire in World War II and how did they impact the empire?
data.meta_description: Answer: The defeats the Ottoman Empire suffered were in WW1 not WW2. In WW1 they were allied with Germany and ended up losing all their remaining empire except present day Turkey.
